apna-program-banaye_key3: Ab iss `file` ko apni pasand ke `editor` se khol kar, kuch content daalte hai
apna-program-banaye_key4: Ab aap iss program ko `execute` karne ki permissions de

apna-program-banaye_key7: Aap apna program kahi se bhi `execute` kar paoge.
